Construction of 25 Nos. 125mm x 40mm x 61m Deep Hand operated tubewell and 8 Nos., 125mm/115mm x 70m deep drilled T/W and  8 nos 125 x 45 M deep gravel packed T/W with I.M.-II Hand Pump, Platform & Drain and 41 Nos. Soakpit in place of old/defunct handpumps in water scarce areas for the year   2022-23 under P.H. Division, Gaya  in district Gaya. 
(i)  125mm x 40mm x 61m Deep Hand operated tubewell - 25 Nos.                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
(ii) 125mm/115mm x 70m deep drilled T/W - 8 Nos
(iii)125 x 45 M deep gravel packed T/W- 8 Nos
(iv)Soak Pit 1.0M diameter 2.0 meter deep with dry brick- 41 Nos
